\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy establishes the governance framework for defining,
 reviewing,
 and acting upon departmental performance metrics and operational key performance indicators (KPIs) used by the Elko County Information Operations Department to evaluate service performance,
 operational resilience,
 security posture,
 and organizational sustainability.
\end_layout

