\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Source-system owner.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
Known data-quality limitations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
Initial KPI selection and all target or threshold changes shall be proposed by the Assistant IT Director and approved by the IT Director before becoming active.
 No KPI shall be added to,
 removed from,
 or redefined within the register without IT Director approval.
\end_layout

