\begin_layout Subsubsection*

\lang english
6.5 Quarterly KPI Review
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
No later than fifteen (15) business days following the close of each calendar quarter,
 the Assistant IT Director shall prepare a Quarterly KPI Review Summary for IT Director review.
 The IT Director shall review the summary and document review acknowledgment.
 The Quarterly KPI Review Summary shall be maintained in the System of Engagement as the authoritative internal record of quarterly KPI governance review.
\end_layout

