 The Monthly Executive Report content is the IT Director's executive communication derivative;
 it draws from,
 but does not replace,
 the quarterly governance record.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
No later than the end of the first calendar quarter following year-end,
 the Assistant IT Director shall prepare an annual KPI and operational performance summary for IT Director approval.
 This summary may be incorporated into the Department's annual reporting or other executive communication issued through County leadership channels.
\end_layout

