\lang english
6.9 Records Retention
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
The Quarterly KPI Review Summary is the authoritative record of KPI governance review.
 Annual executive summaries are derivative communication artifacts and do not replace the quarterly record.
 The Assistant IT Director shall apply retention periods in accordance with NRS 239.125 and the Nevada Local Government Records Retention Schedule.
 The Assistant IT Director shall classify KPI governance records in accordance with 
\series bold
Policy 
