\series default
.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Quarterly KPI Governance Records
\series default
:
 The Assistant IT Director shall retain Quarterly KPI Review Summaries,
 KPI register history documenting target and threshold approvals,
 IT Director review acknowledgments,
 and other quarterly KPI governance records produced under this policy in the System of Engagement for a minimum of three (3) calendar years from the date of production,
 in accordance with LRDA 20071558 (Activity Reports).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
Annual KPI Performance Summaries
\series default
:
 The Assistant IT Director shall retain annual KPI and operational performance summaries that constitute annual activity reports permanently in accordance with LRDA 20071558 (Activity Reports).
\end_layout

